\s Huru kama ndege bustanini
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Huru kama ndege bustanini, sasa nafurahi kwa sababu \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  ni rafiki yangu ’kubwa; nina amani siku zote. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Aliniokoa na mashaka, alinipa tunu ya rehema. Mimi ni mtoto wa babangu, na nuru inang’aa sana. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ninataka ku’shukuru Bwana, alitupa dhambi zangu mbali, na sitaziona tena kamwe, hazitanitawala tena. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Jua likifichwa kwa mawingu, kiti cha rehema ni karibu, hayo ndipo shida ziishapo, na roho yangu yatulia. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Radhi kama mwana kwa babake, kwa salama kama bandarini, Ninapumzika kwa \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd , mbali na shida na huzuni. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Yesu\bd*\bd  yu karibu siku zote, achukua mimi na mzigo. Napokea kwa mkono wake\bd*\bd  Neema \bd*\bd na mateso pia. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Nilimpa \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  moyo wangu, ninapenda kumtumikia; neno lake linapendwa nami, na nira yake ni laini. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Nafurahi sana kanisani kati ya watoto wa babangu, Roho ya\bd*\bd  Neema \bd*\bd ni karibu, kunanifurahisha sana. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mimi ni mdogo duniani, tena msafiri na mgeni. Kwetu ni \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd  huko juu; babangu ananiongoza. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Saa za mashaka zitakwisha, kuja kwake \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  ni karibu. Nitaona raha kubwa sana katika nyumba ya babangu. \bd*
